*** 0.4.0-maki ***
Improve form support :
- modules can "auto manage" forms : submit callbacks added to forms can be auto triggered.

*** 0.3.8-snow ***
Improve form support :
- add submit callback
Improve Session Namespace support :
- add namespace/appname for session
Change Ea_Router in Ea_App ;p
- Ea_Router is still present for compatibility

*** 0.3.7-snow ***
Minor bug fixes :
- correct bug in links.

*** 0.3.6-snow ***
Improve model layout :
- layout model metadata "heritage" from data model.
- you can create layout model without data model.

*** 0.3.5-snow ***
Improve form support :
- redesign of file upload methods.
- add better support for input's name in record table.
- fix session bugs on Ea_Layout_Form::store()
Improve router :
- add app name for session namespaces.
- all sessions are in app namespace.

*** 0.3.4-snow ***
Change version numbering.
Improve security layer :
- add anonymous role.
Improve layer model :
- add postRender() method.
Improve record table :
- add row modifier.

*** 0.0.3.3-dumb ***
Basic batch support.
Multiple select support.
Improve security layer :
- add public role.
- fix minor bug.

*** 0.0.3.2-dumb ***
Improve Zend_Db pdo support in model :
- select statement model support
- support for PDO_OCI data in model
- partial support for Oracle CLOB
Add XML model support :
- model can be load from xml files.

*** 0.0.3.1-dumb ***
Improve form support :
- GET form can be use to build route (search criteria, etc)
Improve layout model :
- header adapter to generate complex headers (ie. sort headers)
Fix bugs on form.

*** 0.0.3.0-dumb ***
Introduce data model in EasyPhpApp :
- EasyPhpApp can now generate record list/form structure from data model (table).

*** 0.0.2.7-guru ***
Improve modularity :
- layouts can now be used outside EasyPhpApp router engine

*** 0.0.2.6-guru ***
Improve security layer :
 - storage of user's defined attributes in session
Improve form support :
 - file upload support

*** 0.0.2.5-guru ***
Improve form support :
 - form structure storage in session
 - inputs can remember last submitted value
 
*** 0.0.2.4-guru ***
Improve form support :
 - radio buttons support